## 3. Story Breakdown

### Story0801 Course Database

Goal:

```text
Create the database foundation for courses, lessons, quizzes, progress, certificates, and learning analytics.
```

Tasks:

```text
Task0801A Design training tables
Task0801B Create Alembic migration
Task0801C Update schema_v1.sql
Task0801D Add demo course seed data
Task0801E Document database changes
```

Acceptance:

```text
training.courses exists
training.lessons exists
training.quizzes exists
training.progress exists
training.certificates exists
Demo course seed data exists
Database documentation is updated
```

### Story0802 Course CRUD

Goal:

```text
Provide course management APIs for creating, updating, listing, publishing, and archiving courses.
```

Tasks:

```text
Task0802A Create course schemas
Task0802B Create course repository
Task0802C Create course service
Task0802D Create course API routes
Task0802E Document course API
```

Acceptance:

```text
Course list API works
Course detail API works
Course create API works
Course update API works
Course publish/archive actions work
API documentation is updated
```

### Story0803 Lesson

Goal:

```text
Support lesson creation, ordering, content editing, and source linkage.
```

Tasks:

```text
Task0803A Create lesson schemas
Task0803B Create lesson service
Task0803C Add lesson ordering
Task0803D Link lessons to SOP/document/experience sources
Task0803E Add demo lessons
```

Acceptance:

```text
Lessons can be created
Lessons can be ordered
Lessons can be updated
Lessons can reference source knowledge
Demo lessons exist
```

### Story0804 Quiz

Goal:

```text
Generate and manage quizzes for lessons and courses.
```

Tasks:

```text
Task0804A Create quiz schemas
Task0804B Create quiz service
Task0804C Add question generation placeholder
Task0804D Add quiz scoring
Task0804E Add demo quiz data
```

Acceptance:

```text
Quiz questions can be created
Quiz questions can be listed
Quiz answers can be scored
Generated quiz demo exists
```

### Story0805 Certificate

Goal:

```text
Issue certificates after course completion and passing score.
```

Tasks:

```text
Task0805A Create certificate service
Task0805B Generate certificate number
Task0805C Add completion rules
Task0805D Add certificate API
Task0805E Add demo certificate
```

Acceptance:

```text
