Certificate has unique number
Certificate links to user and course
Certificate demo data exists
```

### Story0806 AI Mentor

Goal:

```text
Provide AI mentor assistance for learners using course, lesson, SOP, and knowledge context.
```

Tasks:

```text
Task0806A Create mentor context builder
Task0806B Create mentor answer service
Task0806C Link mentor to lessons
Task0806D Add suggested learning questions
Task0806E Document AI mentor behavior
```

Acceptance:

```text
AI mentor endpoint exists
AI mentor uses lesson context
AI mentor suggests follow-up learning questions
Mentor behavior is documented
```

